Finance::YahooJPN::QuoteHist version 0.07
=========================================

 This module provides you functions to fetch historical quote
 of Japanese stock market from Yahoo-Japan-Finance.

INSTALLATION

 To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

 This module and the test script requires internet connection.
 And the test script will take several minutes to progress.
 And sometime the test may fail if the network connection is
 unstable.

DEPENDENCIES

 This module requires perl5.8 or later.
 And,
 this module requires these other modules and libraries:

   LWP::Simple

